Package org.nothing.jocularweather

package org.nothing.jocularweather
  • Class
    Description
    Fetcher
    Class for getting and putting information to weather, storage, and location APIs.
    InfoBox
    Object containing elements to house weather report information.
    LocationBox
    Object containing elements that display current weather information of saved weather locations.
    Logger
    Helper class to log program operation information.
    Main
    Main class for JocularWeather application.
    JocularWeather is a free and open-source software as a service, developed with the goal of making weather data more accessible, light-hearted and enjoyable to those who need it the most.
    MessageType
    Handles types of messages in program console output.
    Report
    Parent class for JSON object from weather report.
    ReportBase
    Interface which handles normally formed and incomplete reports.
    ReportType
    Enumeration for type of report response.
